title: Breakout Second-Year Players & Top 3 QBs in College Football
itunes:title: Breakout Second-Year Players & Top 3 QBs in College Football
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode. To start off, the guys react to the golf game from the weekend which included Tom Brady, Peyton Manning, Tiger Woods and Phil Mickelson (:57). Next, the pair pick which second-year players will take a big jump in 2020 (10:55). To wrap up the show, the duo give their evaluations on the top 3 quarterback prospects in college football (23:02).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
